Package net.automatalib.serialization.taf.parser

Class TAFParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.automatalib.serialization.taf.parser.TAFParser
  • public final class TAFParser
extends Object
    Facade for TAF parsing. This class provides several static methods to read TAF descriptions for DFA and Mealy machines.
